{"tid":1009563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冚家鏟港共01: 政府沒有公布新移民求診數字，冇證據證明新移民逼爆醫院","createTime":"2019-02-05T09:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T12:24:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"38f79311727a3c1e4a174d86375a4e80781a9eaf","tid":1009563,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母弱撚智冇common sense?<br />\n每年幾萬人落嚟係咪數字？<br />\n落咗嚟會唔會唔需要睇醫生？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;而很多人關注的單程證問題，實情是政府從來沒有公布新移民求診數字。不論贊成「新移民逼爆醫院」抑或反對，都難以提出確鑿證據。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局沒有新移民數據<br />\n<br />\n就單證程持有人的求診數字，《香港01》向當局查詢。食物及衛生局表示，這要問醫管局；醫管局則指出，他們對急症室求診人數及住院人數的統計，只會區分「符合資格人士」（EP）及「非符合資格人士」（NEP），而不會記錄或備存他們的居港年期。新移民屬EP之列，但所佔數字是多少，他們無法提供。<br />\n<br />\n當局沒有新移民求診統計，可以反映最少兩點。第一，這令「新移民爆逼醫院」之說無法證實或證偽，無助社會了解真相。&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n俾人屌得多，結論都支持收番審批權cut150係好事<br />\n<br />\n&rsquo;就此而言，《香港01》向來主張政府應收回單程證審批權，並設立一套可應用於受養人簽證的客觀標準，例如家庭團聚的類別、經濟基礎甚至語言能力等。與此同時，政府亦可以考慮檢討單程證每日150個的上限。若能做到這點，政府將可準確預測新移民的社會需要，及早部署社會服務及福利。種種安排，並不能出於任何歧視，而是在尊重中港家庭團聚的實際需要，同時平衡香港社會的承受能力。&lsquo;<br />\n<br />\n不過最後都係想令人既焦點搬離150:<br />\n<br />\n&rsquo;當下公立醫院不勝負荷，只是諸多社會問題之一，還有房屋供應、交通規劃、福利保障等亂象叢生。歸根究柢，香港人應該將矛頭指向誰？&lsquo;<br />\n<br />\n答曰：都係指向150新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/290679/公立醫院逼爆-是新移民的錯?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F290679%2F%E5%85%AC%E7%AB%8B%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A2%E9%80%BC%E7%88%86-%E6%98%AF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=494f73f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01觀點/290679/公立醫院逼爆-是新移民的錯?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a>"},{"pid":"b86d5cd74d62d18e5e4e2a36172002c393a253af","tid":1009563,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:17:29.000Z","msg":"冇證據證明新移民逼爆醫院<br />\n=/=<br />\n有證據證明<span style=\"color: red;\">新移民冇逼爆醫院</span><br />\n<br />\n支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98436dbf6a4bd60cd3fd80b04699cf4e2b0876c2","tid":1009563,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:19:42.000Z","msg":"參考了 2017年11月保安局向立法會提交和統計處公佈的單程證年齡分佈數字，我將數據對比過香港本身的人口年齡分佈，發現相差根本不大，<br />\n<br />\n若以2017年來港單程證為例，更見到24歲以下實際僅得3成多，而45歲以上的佔逾23%，其中65歲以上更過千人！<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，在政府沒有審批權的情況下，單程證沒法令社會更年輕，反而一直增加老年人口的實際數量，加重香港社會醫療、福利負擔。大陸的長者，應由大陸政府承擔照顧的責任，而不是香港的醫療體系。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">單是2007年至2017年間，單程證就為香港帶來了7萬7千多個45歲或以上的人口。我不能說他們一來到香港便生病及求醫，但只要其中15%曾一年到一次公立醫院，已產生每年過萬人次的求醫個案，實在地加劇了公營醫院的負擔。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1009526\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1009526</a>"},{"pid":"1a42c879b451287d39427d947414857f8d7a3b19","tid":1009563,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈要求引入中國醫生</span> </span></strong><br />\n五千年黎中國偉大文化 一定要入引中國醫生解決香港班仆街醫生<br />\n好撚唔抵得佢地咁高人工，一定要拉到佢1萬5千蚊一個月 低過洗碗阿姐！！！！！！ 大家一齊跟我大字報<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孕婦剖腹產子被偷腎 中國新華醫院院長供認曾偷九個腎<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=6476d197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20120829%2F18002608&h=24a56f2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20120829/18002608</a><br />\n<br />\n手術後腎消失 農婦尋腎3年無果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2015%2F01%2F29%2Fa1172952.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=365f1fe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2015/01/29/a1172952.html</a><br />\n<br />\n包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！ 病人負傷起來繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=1eb672af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F882584-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E5%89%B2%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%81%9C%E4%B8%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B91%E8%90%AC5%EF%BC%81%2B%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B7%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E7%B9%B3%E8%B2%BB&h=c41842b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/882584-中國-包皮手術割一半醫生停下加價1萬5！+病人負傷起來繳費</a><br />\n<br />\n重慶醫生手術途中突加碼　費用飆升13倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20151130%2Fbkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=17da5d67\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20151130/bkncn-20151130041046031-1130_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇男割包皮　醫生手術中加價5倍　院方：沒違規 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=8910a991\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20181205%2Fs00004%2F1543977455217%2F%E6%B1%9F%E8%98%87%E7%94%B7%E5%89%B2%E5%8C%85%E7%9A%AE-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%83%B95%E5%80%8D-%E9%99%A2%E6%96%B9-%E6%B2%92%E9%81%95%E8%A6%8F&h=3aa50e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20181205/s00004/1543977455217/江蘇男割包皮-醫生手術中加價5倍-院方-沒違規</a><br />\n<br />\n成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦　警方：嫌犯現已被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F191422%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%89%8B%E8%A1%93%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%9F%E8%A2%AB%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9-%E5%AB%8C%E7%8A%AF%E7%8F%BE%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=e1b24131\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/191422/成都女子手術麻醉後竟被醫生強姦-警方-嫌犯現已被捕</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8F%E4%BA%8B%2F288428%2F%E6%88%90%E9%83%BD%E7%84%A1%E7%89%8C%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E5%B0%87%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%BA%BB%E9%86%89%E5%BE%8C%E5%BC%B7%E5%A7%A6-%E5%A4%9A%E9%A0%85%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%916%E5%B9%B44%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFq0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=8fcfe11f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/大國小事/288428/成都無牌醫生將女患者麻醉後強姦-多項罪成獲刑6年4個月</a><br />\n<br />\n辦案人員經查發現，羅平沒有取得醫師資格證和醫師執業證。他於2017年6月開始在雙流區某街道開設的「1+1服務中心」從事醫療活動，並辦理虛假的醫師資格證、醫師執業證和身份證，向雙流區某醫院提交。他又於2016年至2018年期間，階段性在雙流某醫院坐診。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">強姦、偷腎、加價 、假醫生，少不免 沒事兒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/re0xvoV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fre0xvoV.gif&h=9fbdef6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強國黨媒展視中國式CPR 救助心臟停頓病人<br />\n－＞未來香港將會獲得優秀中國式醫療！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUF5Qo9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUF5Qo9.jpg&h=7dca3fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">建議香港政府先提出引入英國醫生 <br />\n然後再偷偷地引入大陸醫生<br />\n咁樣就可以拉低醫生人工<br />\n我最想見到既事情先會發生！！！<br />\n我要佢地死、低人工過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n自2012年起，醫管局以有限度註冊聘請了39名海外醫生來港執業，但截至2018年底只有10名仍在公立醫院服務，「事實是醫管局無法挽留本港的畢業醫生，也無法挽留海外畢業的醫生。」<br />\n<br />\n林晢玄早前接受訪問時指，可參考新加坡模式，讓指定院校名單的海外醫生免試到本港公立醫院工作，年期不限。有關建議可謂是「改良版」的有限度註冊制度。<br />\n<br />\n而公共醫療醫生協會今日（30日）再發表聲明，指歡迎任何擁有與本港同等專業資格的海外畢業醫生，遵從現有機制，且透過有限度註冊來港，但需確保海外醫生長期留在公立醫院。<br />\n<br />\n香港公共醫療醫生協會稱，政府在2003年沙士削減2667張病床、推俗稱「肥雞餐」的自願離職計劃、關閉護士學校、削減醫科學額，緊縮醫療開資，而這些措施的惡果終在十多年後出現。協會指香港公營醫療體系早就超出負荷，而醫院的工作環境已達不安全水平，嚴重危害病人安全及影響服務質素，而前線醫護仍一直努力工作，「哀我同業，咫尺但愁雷雨至，向來悲傷何其多？」<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以香港戰地環境引入高質英國醫生！<br />\n可能外國鬼佬鍾意戰地環境同埋語言挑戰</span></strong></span><br />\n大中華呢3個字已經夠吸引佢地<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢地NHS d醫院 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJYOBJo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJYOBJo.jpg&h=b6235a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrxvP3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrxvP3q.jpg&h=62b8bafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4knr7P6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4knr7P6.jpg&h=d20ccc63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b60UxgO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb60UxgO.jpg&h=af70738c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MYP95BR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMYP95BR.jpg&h=2b03b738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地香港d醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQWHGas.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQWHGas.jpg&h=eb01e00e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qyJGcg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqyJGcg9.jpg&h=a2c8d832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xsLDXa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xsLDXa.jpg&h=ca2fec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Skczxhm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSkczxhm.jpg&h=ed64d856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tjeexhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeexhq.jpg&h=ac181a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">英聯邦高質醫生一定好鍾意挑戰自己 快d邀請佢地黎香港做野</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"5b471e171c7edf5ab68097a16d9bb6c31dc2a423","tid":1009563,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b86d5cd74d62d18e5e4e2a36172002c393a253af","tid":1009563,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:17:29.000Z","msg":"冇證據證明新移民逼爆醫院<br />\n=/=<br />\n有證據證明<span style=\"color: red;\">新移民冇逼爆醫院</span><br />\n<br />\n支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:22:33.000Z","msg":"多咗成百萬人口<br />\n就算同本地人類近使用量都多咗十幾%需求<br />\n何況可能唔止<br />\n<br />\nBtw仲未計自由行落嚟生仔打針"},{"pid":"07eb581e19a9a99ee85f3c2c36e924b4b32dd09f","tid":1009563,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"祝支那01仝人全家出街俾車車死<br />\n<br />\n仲要係大陸車 確保轆死晒全家先走"},{"pid":"b8e66872c5a584c938573f92030a933a640b340e","tid":1009563,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"746250d23ffedb5bdbff95e473dd7eba25e5bcd7","tid":1009563,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:43:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5fa45aebb1764b10906b3d4dc39bbee90a6c21","tid":1009563,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T09:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce3945387b1d397a09d61b34dc1973fb51eb36e","tid":1009563,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T12:24:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}